(4443, 70, 'section_builder_0_layout_section_full_width_content', 'Groundswell is a growing online community of nearly 100,000 people who believe faith can be a force for good in the world. Faith-rooted leaders, organizers, and others motivated by faith and moral commitment come to Groundswell to be inspired to take faithful action, to learn how to organize in a digital age, and to use cutting-edge tools to support their work healing and repairing the world.'),
