(5447, 2, 'landing_page_sub_intro_content', '<div class="col-sm-12">\r\n\r\nGroundswell is a growing online community of nearly 100,000 people who believe faith can be a force for good in the world. Faith-rooted leaders, organizers, and others motivated by faith and moral commitment come to Groundswell to be inspired to take faithful action, to learn how to organize in a digital age, and to use cutting-edge tools to support their work healing and repairing the world.\r\n\r\n</div>'),
